8	-- -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
9	-- Data types for working with AXI4-Lite interfaces.
10	-- Based on the document "ARM IHI 0022E (ID022613): AMBA AXI and ACE Protocol Specification"
11	-- Available here: http://infocenter.arm.com/help/index.jsp?topic=/com.arm.doc.ihi0022e/
12	-- -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
